Scenario-Based SQL Questions
Example 1
Find the 2nd highest salary.
SELECT MAX(salary)
FROM employee
WHERE salary < (
   SELECT MAX(salary)
   FROM employee
);

Example 2
Find duplicate records.
SELECT name, COUNT(*)
FROM employee
GROUP BY name
HAVING COUNT(*) > 1;
